text: Isabela Moner (born July 10, 2001), also known as Isabela Merced, is an American actor and singer. She played the lead role of CJ Martin on the Nickelodeon television show 100 Things to Do Before High School. She played Izabella in the movie Transformers: The Last Knight (2017), Lizzy in Instant Family (2018), and Isabel in Sicario: Day of the Soldado (2018). In 2019, Moner played Dora in the movie Dora and the Lost City of Gold. From 2014 to 2017, she was the voice of Kate in Nickelodeon's animated television show Dora and Friends: Into the City!. == References == Category:2001 births Category:Actors from Cleveland Category:American child actors Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American video game actors Category:American voice actors Category:Living people Category:Singers from Ohio Category:Stage actors
